,"msg":"唔罰埋個撚樣技工坐監？"},{"pid":"5ae4519cc65e46be6b9245bb47d078c22ebc41aa","tid":587001,"uid":52943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-10T05:38:35.000Z","msg":"32萬<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"203fba61fc865286d42d7d8b1658a33a7de80260","tid":587001,"uid":46332,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-10T05:45:27.000Z","msg":"咁有冇交代到果四日d人去左邊?"},{"pid":"412e7967b9629fd558cecfd437a7c145cc84c0b7","tid":587001,"uid":65061,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-10T05:46:22.000Z","msg":"哇 三十二萬 好撚多呀 夠唔夠高層出一個月花紅<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"805c5d30b94591fb78ed137463ae3269ffb5f8d9","tid":587001,"uid":39381,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-10T05:47:37.000Z","msg":"3千2百萬就差唔多<br />\n32萬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0c39e19de035e3f3e14c8491f6e9c3602205589a","tid":587001,"uid":40272,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5a13422bb75841718b838f248ccd69d779671a6c","tid":587001,"uid":100136,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-10T05:32:51.000Z","msg":"唔罰埋個撚樣技工坐監？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-10T08:06:33.000Z","msg":"無撚人敢入行<br />\n政府好撚驚 到時要行樓梯<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}